title: Gos Ultimate edition
description:
Gos (Good OS) is the software that comes with the $200 Everex gPC sold at Walmart.

It is the sleek and simple Linux operating system built on Ubuntu making use of the beautiful E17 desktop environment.  
Get more info at www.thinkgos.com 

This is the same as the Rocket beta edition, but with a few neat tweaks.  Be aware, that this is a beta edition.  Even the E17 desktop environment is beta.  That means things will not work as well as they should.  Still, this OS serves as a perfect alternative to Windows for those computer users who only need to "get online" and is a terrific way to make that 9-year-old computer work like new again!  Custom Mac-style links at the bottom for the most popular applications and sites!
